{"tid":1369582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府高官入一入黎","createTime":"2019-07-26T17:34:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T18:31:26.000Z","uid":9435,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0e61b8c25a243d3f8109849c162016e4eb71f289","tid":1369582,"uid":9435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:34:28.000Z","msg":"你地行得用張建宗呢步棋,我都唔介意比條明路你地行<br />\n你地都係幫張建宗加分,拉林奠落黎,佢上馬姐<br />\n可以呢步棋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n張建宗上任之後可以大大聲上任特首既任務已經完滿結束(你班仆街都會講撒回架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n之後話餘下任期會重啟雙普選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n獨立調查委員會大勢所趨,順應民意又係要做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後就係唔起訴所有義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n政府開始回應市民訴求<br />\n姐係我地方向正確<br />\n各界手足出聲明既繼續出聲明<br />\n罷工繼續罷工<br />\n要聯署既繼續聯署<br />\n5大訴求..回應哂就會變返港豬架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42efdd144d1b0ab4fc6708425994d92134fbeaf5","tid":1369582,"uid":9435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:34:59.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"bec0c7323c7546c14c430a3d1156bfa6124ee708","tid":1369582,"uid":9435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:52:35.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"4b934d0f71306d6437a6ae670b7551b79735854a","tid":1369582,"uid":9435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:09:00.000Z","msg":"光復香港,時代革命"},{"pid":"84b1e521697c81ae4163c98ef31de28793eb3f13","tid":1369582,"uid":14087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:09:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/a